Recommended Learning Roadmap

If your goal is to become an AI Engineer, MLOps Engineer, or DevOps Engineer, a practical sequence is:

Git & GitHub
Docker
Nginx
Jenkins
Ansible
Terraform or OpenTofu
Kubernetes
Helm
Argo CD
Prometheus + Grafana
OpenFaaS or Knative (Serverless)
Full MLOps workflows with Kubernetes

This progression takes you from deploying a single application on one machine to operating large-scale,
production-grade AI systems used by organizations around the world.

